Mntucing hngkawas 1952 idas 6 jiyax 18 ka Idriss Déby ga, empklaw ka hiya.

Bukung klwaan [[Chad]] ta sayang o kiya ka Idriss Déby, pnaah hngkawas 1990 idas 12 jiyax 2 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.

